data.description: Stop throwing away rent money and invest in this beautiful town home! This fashionable town home is beautifully appointed and the location is phenomenal. Stroll to the Tacoma Mall, restaurants and more. Once inside you'll find a lovely living room with gas fireplace, large kitchen and two nice sized bedrooms. Both with their own baths. The laundry room is upstairs for easy access. Lots of storage! Buy now! There are four identical units available.
